<subSubSection id="C347651CFFB0F847FF192093FCF1F8D3" pageId="1" pageNumber="436" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BE23697FFB0F847FF192093FB72F97C" blockId="1.[151,1437,1482,1870]" pageId="1" pageNumber="436">
<emphasis id="B929EA85FFB0F847FF192093FEBFF921" bold="true" box="[199,338,1698,1724]" pageId="1" pageNumber="436">Comments:</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="4C5D4D14FFB0F847FE852092FE29F920" authorityName="Mannerheim" authorityYear="1837" box="[347,452,1699,1725]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Conognatha" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="436" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="lebasii">
<emphasis id="B929EA85FFB0F847FE852092FE29F920" box="[347,452,1699,1725]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="436">S. lebasii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was originally described by 
<bibRefCitation id="EFCC4B66FFB0F847FCCC2092FC1AF920" author="Mannerheim" box="[786,1015,1699,1725]" firstAuthor="Mannerheim" pageId="1" pageNumber="436" pagination="1 - 126" refId="ref2290" refString="Mannerheim, C. G. von (1837) Enumeration des Buprestides, et description de quelques nouvelles especes de cette tribu de la famille des Sternoxes, de la collection de M. Le Comte Mannerheim. Bulletin de la Societe Imperiale des Naturalistes des Moscou, 8, 1 - 126." type="journal article" year="1837">Mannerheim (1837)</bibRefCitation>
, who assigned the authorship of this species to Dejean, but it actually belongs to 
<bibRefCitation id="EFCC4B66FFB0F847FD5B20F6FC85F97C" author="Mannerheim" box="[645,872,1735,1761]" firstAuthor="Mannerheim" pageId="1" pageNumber="436" pagination="1 - 126" refId="ref2290" refString="Mannerheim, C. G. von (1837) Enumeration des Buprestides, et description de quelques nouvelles especes de cette tribu de la famille des Sternoxes, de la collection de M. Le Comte Mannerheim. Bulletin de la Societe Imperiale des Naturalistes des Moscou, 8, 1 - 126." type="journal article" year="1837">Mannerheim (1837)</bibRefCitation>
, who wrote the description.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BE23697FFB0F847FF1920DAFCF1F8D3" blockId="1.[151,1437,1482,1870]" pageId="1" pageNumber="436">
It was described from a specimen sent to 
<collectorName id="26A85341FFB0F847FD4B20DAFC7AF898" box="[661,919,1771,1797]" pageId="1" pageNumber="436">C. G. von Mannerheim</collectorName>
by 
<collectorName id="26A85341FFB0F847FC1E20DAFB42F898" box="[960,1199,1771,1797]" pageId="1" pageNumber="436">M. Le Comte Dejean</collectorName>
, which was collected in “ 
<collectingCountry id="F34A7607FFB0F847FF63213EFE88F8B4" box="[189,357,1807,1833]" name="Colombia" pageId="1" pageNumber="436">Nova Granada</collectingCountry>
; ad 
<superScript id="7C289BDFFFB0F847FE4C213EFE40F880" attach="left" box="[402,429,1807,1833]" fontSize="6" pageId="1" pageNumber="436">Sta</superScript>
. Fé di 
<collectingRegion id="4999F875FFB0F847FE24213EFDBCF8B4" box="[506,593,1807,1833]" country="Colombia" name="Bogota" pageId="1" pageNumber="436">Bogota</collectingRegion>
.” by 
<collectorName id="26A85341FFB0F847FD59213EFD19F8B4" box="[647,756,1807,1833]" pageId="1" pageNumber="436">M. Lebas</collectorName>
, to whom the species was dedicated. The 
<typeStatus id="54E68835FFB0F847FB1B213EFAC1F8B4" box="[1221,1324,1807,1833]" pageId="1" pageNumber="436">lectotype</typeStatus>
housed at the 
<collectionCode id="ED4CAE52FFB0F847FF1E2102FEE3F8D0" box="[192,270,1843,1869]" pageId="1" pageNumber="436">MZHF</collectionCode>
is labelled as “ 
<location id="8E82604CFFB0F847FE662102FE16F8D0" LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:03F48781FFB0F847FF4923FBFCF1F8D3:8E82604CFFB0F847FE662102FE16F8D0" box="[440,507,1843,1869]" country="Colombia" name="St. Fe" pageId="1" pageNumber="436" stateProvince="Bogota">St. Fé</location>
di 
<collectingRegion id="4999F875FFB0F847FDC02102FD9FF8D0" box="[542,626,1843,1869]" country="Colombia" name="Bogota" pageId="1" pageNumber="436">Bogota</collectingRegion>
” (
<collectorName id="26A85341FFB0F847FD542102FD36F8D0" box="[650,731,1843,1869]" pageId="1" pageNumber="436">Dejean</collectorName>
leg.).
</paragraph>
